aa(lp171
VAll right, well, what about online dating?
p172
aVI mean, that's a pretty deceptive space.
p173
aVI'm sure you all have "friends" that have used online dating. (Laughter)
p174
aVAnd they would tell you about that guy that had no hair
p175
aVwhen he came, or the woman that didn't look at all like her photo.
