aVWell, we were really interested in it, and so what we did
p177
aVis we brought people, online daters, into the lab,
p178
aVand then we measured them. We got their height
p179
aVup against the wall, we put them on a scale, got their weight \u2014
p180
aVladies loved that \u2014 and then we actually got their driver's license to get their age.
